<h2 style="text-align: center; border-radius: 20px; margin-bottom: 30px; background-color: #337ab7; padding: 5px; font-size: 72px; font-family: 'Times New Roman' ;">Código Braille</h2>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-4" style="margin-top:30px">
